    "raw": "\n<p style=\"font-size:22px\">When cables are cut, sanctions are put in place or privacy legislation prohibits the use of the service your entire organization depends on, what can you do?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Amidst geo-political changes, organizations face dependencies on large, centralized communication platforms. A major example of this is the SaaS-only communication platform Microsoft Teams. It is the only solution on the market which deeply integrates video calls, team chat and large group call features with real-time document collaboration and file sharing, and has become critical to the functioning of many organizations. Which, in turn, has allowed Microsoft to hike prices by 20 to 40% and not face an exodus of customers – as they and their data are fully locked in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Organisations, small and large, need a way to ensure the resiliency and digital sovereignty of their operations – an open source, privacy respecting alternative to Teams. And today, we present that solution.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Introducing the Open Source answer to Microsoft Teams\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1035504262?h=776fa1186e&amp;dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In this short webinar, Jos walks you through how Nextcloud Talk takes on Microsoft Teams!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-top\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 22%\"><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Welcome to Nextcloud Talk</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Today, live from our Enterprise day in Paris, we launch Nextcloud Talk „Paris“. It is the <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/talk/#compare\">only open-source solution that integrates all key features</a> – from chats and video conferencing to webinars, complete with file sharing and office document editing – into a single platform while avoiding vendor lock-in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our platform meets the highest standards of compliance with privacy legislations like GDPR or HIPAA and offers strict data security, ensuring full data control. Thanks to its open architecture, Talk can be seamlessly integrated into existing systems and tailored to individual needs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nextcloud Talk is designed to address three key use cases. Let’s go quickly over them!</p>\n</div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"160\" height=\"160\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Nextcloud-Talk-1.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-273429 size-full\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Efficient team chat</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The integrated chat in Nextcloud Talk is designed to help teams stay connected throughout the workday. With multiple chat rooms and the ability to edit files directly within the chat, Talk streamlines hybrid team collaboration and boosts efficiency. End-to-end encryption ensures that calls remain private and secure, while integrated real-time notifications keep everyone in the loop. All data stays under your control, meeting the highest privacy and security standards.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It features deep integration with a wide variety of content. Users can add documents &#8211; and edit them right there, inline, without having to open tabs or download the file. Locations, tasks, calendars and notes can all be inserted, viewed and edited without leaving Talk.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n<section class=\"simple-slider-section \" id=\"\">\n\t<div class=\"\">\n                    <div class=\"owl-carousel simple_slider_slideshow\" id=\"\">\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"271779\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-Rich-Widgets-edit-documents-in-line-copy.jpg\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-Rich-Widgets-edit-documents-in-line-copy.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-Rich-Widgets-edit-documents-in-line-copy.jpg 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-Rich-Widgets-edit-documents-in-line-copy-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-Rich-Widgets-edit-documents-in-line-copy-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-Rich-Widgets-edit-documents-in-line-copy-768x432.jpg 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-Rich-Widgets-edit-documents-in-line-copy-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"271769\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Hub-9-Talk-all-smart-picker-items-copy.jpg\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Hub-9-Talk-all-smart-picker-items-copy.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Hub-9-Talk-all-smart-picker-items-copy.jpg 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Hub-9-Talk-all-smart-picker-items-copy-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Hub-9-Talk-all-smart-picker-items-copy-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Hub-9-Talk-all-smart-picker-items-copy-768x432.jpg 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Hub-9-Talk-all-smart-picker-items-copy-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"271764\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-ai-summary-unread-messages-mockup-copy.jpg\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-ai-summary-unread-messages-mockup-copy.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-ai-summary-unread-messages-mockup-copy.jpg 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-ai-summary-unread-messages-mockup-copy-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-ai-summary-unread-messages-mockup-copy-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-ai-summary-unread-messages-mockup-copy-768x432.jpg 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-ai-summary-unread-messages-mockup-copy-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"271748\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary.png\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Nextcloud Talk AI summary\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary.png 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary-300x169.png 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary-1024x576.png 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary-768x432.png 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                            </ul>\n        \t</div>\n</section>\n<script type=\"rocketlazyloadscript\">\n    jQuery(document).ready(function ($) {\n        var owl_simple_slider = $('.simple_slider_slideshow');\n        owl_simple_slider.owlCarousel({\n            loop:true,\n            stagePadding: 50,\n            autoplay: true,\n            margin:10,\n            dots: false,\n            nav:true,\n            responsive:{\n                0:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                600:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                800:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                1000:{\n                    items:1\n                }\n            },\n            onDragged: owl_stop_autoplay,\n            autoplayHoverPause:true\n        });\n\n        owl_simple_slider.on('click', function(e) {\n            owl_stop_autoplay();\n        });\n        function owl_stop_autoplay() {\n            //console.log('autoplay stopped.');\n            owl_simple_slider.trigger('stop.owl.autoplay');\n        }\n\n    });\n</script>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Video calls for seamless collaboration</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Nextcloud Talk makes virtual meetings easy and accessible across devices. Whether it’s a quick check-in or a larger team meeting, our platform ensures powerful collaboration for hybrid working teams. Features like integrated whiteboards, screen sharing, and joint document editing make real-time collaboration easier than ever. Scheduling and joining calls is effortless, directly from the Nextcloud interface, integrated with the calendar app for easy scheduling of meetings.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n<section class=\"simple-slider-section \" id=\"\">\n\t<div class=\"\">\n                    <div class=\"owl-carousel simple_slider_slideshow\" id=\"\">\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"273042\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-screenshot-call-grid-view-1.png\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"6400\" height=\"3600\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-screenshot-call-grid-view-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-screenshot-call-grid-view-1.png 6400w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-screenshot-call-grid-view-1-300x169.png 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-screenshot-call-grid-view-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-screenshot-call-grid-view-1-768x432.png 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-screenshot-call-grid-view-1-1536x864.png 1536w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-screenshot-call-grid-view-1-2048x1152.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 6400px) 100vw, 6400px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"207898\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/04/Nextcloud-Talk-Screensharing-bubble-camera-and-poll-popup.jpg\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/04/Nextcloud-Talk-Screensharing-bubble-camera-and-poll-popup.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Nextcloud Talk Screensharing bubble camera and poll popup\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/04/Nextcloud-Talk-Screensharing-bubble-camera-and-poll-popup.jpg 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/04/Nextcloud-Talk-Screensharing-bubble-camera-and-poll-popup-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/04/Nextcloud-Talk-Screensharing-bubble-camera-and-poll-popup-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/04/Nextcloud-Talk-Screensharing-bubble-camera-and-poll-popup-768x432.jpg 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/04/Nextcloud-Talk-Screensharing-bubble-camera-and-poll-popup-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"257451\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Hub-9-Talking-time-on-participants-in-call-with-avatars-and-reactions-web.jpg\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Hub-9-Talking-time-on-participants-in-call-with-avatars-and-reactions-web.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Nextcloud Hub 9 - Talk video conferencing\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Hub-9-Talking-time-on-participants-in-call-with-avatars-and-reactions-web.jpg 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Hub-9-Talking-time-on-participants-in-call-with-avatars-and-reactions-web-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Hub-9-Talking-time-on-participants-in-call-with-avatars-and-reactions-web-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Hub-9-Talking-time-on-participants-in-call-with-avatars-and-reactions-web-768x432.jpg 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Hub-9-Talking-time-on-participants-in-call-with-avatars-and-reactions-web-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"252936\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Nextcloud-Hub-9-Whiteboard-screenshots-basic-actions_02.png\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Nextcloud-Hub-9-Whiteboard-screenshots-basic-actions_02.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Nextcloud Hub 9 Whiteboard basic actions\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Nextcloud-Hub-9-Whiteboard-screenshots-basic-actions_02.png 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Nextcloud-Hub-9-Whiteboard-screenshots-basic-actions_02-300x169.png 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Nextcloud-Hub-9-Whiteboard-screenshots-basic-actions_02-1024x576.png 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Nextcloud-Hub-9-Whiteboard-screenshots-basic-actions_02-768x432.png 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/09/Nextcloud-Hub-9-Whiteboard-screenshots-basic-actions_02-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                            </ul>\n        \t</div>\n</section>\n<script type=\"rocketlazyloadscript\">\n    jQuery(document).ready(function ($) {\n        var owl_simple_slider = $('.simple_slider_slideshow');\n        owl_simple_slider.owlCarousel({\n            loop:true,\n            stagePadding: 50,\n            autoplay: true,\n            margin:10,\n            dots: false,\n            nav:true,\n            responsive:{\n                0:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                600:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                800:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                1000:{\n                    items:1\n                }\n            },\n            onDragged: owl_stop_autoplay,\n            autoplayHoverPause:true\n        });\n\n        owl_simple_slider.on('click', function(e) {\n            owl_stop_autoplay();\n        });\n        function owl_stop_autoplay() {\n            //console.log('autoplay stopped.');\n            owl_simple_slider.trigger('stop.owl.autoplay');\n        }\n\n    });\n</script>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Interactive webinars, education and training sessions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Talk enables you to host engaging webinars – bringing audiences like teams, students, or customers together. The platform supports live streaming, Q&amp;A sessions and screensharing and comes with moderation features. Functions like the integrated chat, animated reactions, polls and breakout rooms make the learning experience more interactive and fun. All this, and more, is available wherever you are. Not only in the browser, but also with apps on iOS and Android! When your colleague calls you while you’re out, your phone will ring and you’ll be able to share your screen to show them a quick presentation you’re working on.</p>\n\n\n<section class=\"simple-slider-section \" id=\"\">\n\t<div class=\"\">\n                    <div class=\"owl-carousel simple_slider_slideshow\" id=\"\">\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"271774\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-webinar-in-action-copy.jpg\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-webinar-in-action-copy.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-webinar-in-action-copy.jpg 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-webinar-in-action-copy-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-webinar-in-action-copy-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-webinar-in-action-copy-768x432.jpg 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-webinar-in-action-copy-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"271754\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-call-presenting-copy.jpg\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-call-presenting-copy.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-call-presenting-copy.jpg 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-call-presenting-copy-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-call-presenting-copy-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-call-presenting-copy-768x432.jpg 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-call-presenting-copy-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"gallery_item\" id=\"271759\">\n                        <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-room-moderation-settings-copy.jpg\" class=\"simple_slider_slideshow_link\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-room-moderation-settings-copy.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-room-moderation-settings-copy.jpg 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-room-moderation-settings-copy-300x169.jpg 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-room-moderation-settings-copy-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-room-moderation-settings-copy-768x432.jpg 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Talk-room-moderation-settings-copy-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" />                        </a>\n                                            </div>\n                            </ul>\n        \t</div>\n</section>\n<script type=\"rocketlazyloadscript\">\n    jQuery(document).ready(function ($) {\n        var owl_simple_slider = $('.simple_slider_slideshow');\n        owl_simple_slider.owlCarousel({\n            loop:true,\n            stagePadding: 50,\n            autoplay: true,\n            margin:10,\n            dots: false,\n            nav:true,\n            responsive:{\n                0:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                600:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                800:{\n                    items:1\n                },\n                1000:{\n                    items:1\n                }\n            },\n            onDragged: owl_stop_autoplay,\n            autoplayHoverPause:true\n        });\n\n        owl_simple_slider.on('click', function(e) {\n            owl_stop_autoplay();\n        });\n        function owl_stop_autoplay() {\n            //console.log('autoplay stopped.');\n            owl_simple_slider.trigger('stop.owl.autoplay');\n        }\n\n    });\n</script>\n\n\n\n<p>You can give participants a phone number to dial in to, and even pull them in by dialing out right from Talk. Need to add hundreds, even thousands of participants? Simply import a spreadsheet. After the call, you export the participant list and see who did and did not show up!</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Add user by email in Nextcloud Talk\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1035699520?h=3d9db32f5a&amp;dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Break up big groups in breakout rooms, enabling everyone to be productive in a smaller team before coming back together to the big group. In your breakout room you can do a call, chat, work on a whiteboard, share documents and more!</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Power your team meeting using breakout rooms!\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1035528263?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Numerous new features for better collaboration</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">New desktop app</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No more searching through browser tabs! The new app offers desktop integration and notifications, allowing users to communicate and join calls effortlessly.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"720\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Laptop_07-720x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-272981\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Laptop_07-720x576.png 720w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Laptop_07-300x240.png 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Laptop_07-768x614.png 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Laptop_07-1536x1229.png 1536w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Laptop_07-2048x1638.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">New AI features</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Tired of taking notes in long meetings? Enjoy our automatically generated summaries of video meetings! Dreading those 173 unread messages in the morning? The Nextcloud Assistant summarizes them for you. Less work, less stress!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full imageRoundShadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary.png\" alt=\"Nextcloud Talk AI summary\" class=\"wp-image-271748\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary.png 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary-300x169.png 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary-1024x576.png 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary-768x432.png 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/11/Nextcloud-Talk-AI-summary-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Visual collaboration</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The interactive whiteboard enables teams to brainstorm and develop ideas in real-time – ideal for workshops and project planning.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Collaborative real-time sketching with Nextcloud Whiteboard\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xfzu98kPdh0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Plan your polls</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can now save a poll as a draft, for quick publishing when the class has started. Need to use the same poll in a different class? Simply export it as a file and import it in the new room. At the end, export the poll as image or spreadsheet. Easy as pie!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Creating a conversation summary in Nextcloud Talk using Desktop Client\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1034529231?h=101e8c7083&amp;dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simplified teamwork</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Documents can be collaboratively edited directly within chats or video calls. No need to switch to another window or tab! You can easily find chat messages with the search, leave and join open chat rooms or archive the ones you no longer follow, so you stay as connected as you need to be.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let colleagues know what you think with reactions to chat messages, or animated reactions during calls. And if you need to make a point, you can use <strong>bold</strong>, <em>italics</em>, headers and even tables in your messages.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"How you don&#039;t need to leave your chat with Talk\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/1034532206?h=a5e24cce23&amp;dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mindfulness features</h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"alignright size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"507\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-reminder-on-message-crop-507x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-272811\" style=\"width:224px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-reminder-on-message-crop-507x576.png 507w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-reminder-on-message-crop-264x300.png 264w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-reminder-on-message-crop-768x873.png 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-reminder-on-message-crop-1352x1536.png 1352w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/12/Talk-reminder-on-message-crop.png 1712w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 507px) 100vw, 507px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>To promote a healthy meeting culture, Nextcloud Talk has a series of small features that help you be mindful of yourself and others. You can send silent chat messages and even start silent calls which don&#8217;t send notifications to everyone. User status communicates to colleagues if you&#8217;re available or not &#8211; the status will automatically change when you are in a call or have an appointment in your calendar, and your time zone is visible for others.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need to deal with something &#8211; but not right now? You can mark a chat as unread, but also set a reminder on an individual message. You&#8217;ll get a notification at the time you set! You can also send a message to a special &#8216;Note to self&#8217; chat, or put notes there by hand. Keep things organized for yourself. Perhaps favorite your Note to self chat so it&#8217;s always on top with other important chats?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also set your work hours and enable do-not-disturb outside those hours. Calls give a warning at the 1h mark and can now automatically end after a set time. And, during calls, you can see how much each participant talked so you can make sure even the quiet team members get to have their say.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">High-security communication</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Nextcloud Talk meets the highest security standards and can even be deployed in airgap environments, keeping all communication strictly away from the internet.</p>\n\n\n\n<details class=\"wp-block-details is-layout-flow wp-block-details-is-layout-flow\"><summary>Discover more new features</summary>\n<p>Calls:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Summarize Call recordings automatically with AI</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Enforce a maximum call lenght</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Option to always disable devices by default</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Option to download a call participants list</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Option to blur background by default</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Chat:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Summary of chat histories when there are many unread messages</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Option to directly download attachments</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Highlight file and object shares with an icon in conversations list</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Guests:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Identify and recognize guests invited via mail address</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Allow inviting email guests when creating a conversation</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Conversations:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Option to archive conversations</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Automatically lock rooms after days of inactivity</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Voice Messages:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Auto play voice messages which are grouped together</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Polls:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Draft, import and export polls</li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:29px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A glimpse into the future of collaboration</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With Nextcloud Talk, we empower companies and public institutions to work securely and productively – regardless of their location or infrastructure. The platform is ideal for on-premises installations or hosting by local cloud providers, giving companies and organizations full control over their data.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, the open source community has a real answer to Microsoft Teams. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more at the <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/talk\">Talk webpage</a>, or <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/blog/event/nextcloud-talk-paris-microsoft-teams-alternative/\">join our upcoming webinar</a> to find out how Talk can replace Teams for your organization!</p>\n\n\n<section class=\"promo-section promo_webinar has_custom_bg_image  full-width \" id=\"\" style=\"\">\n\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-block \">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Get started with Nextcloud Talk</h2><p>Learn more about Nextcloud Talk and get started right away!</p>\n<a class=\"c-btn btn-white\" href=\"https://nextcloud.com/talk/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/blog/nextcloud-talk-our-open-source-answer-to-microsoft-teams/\">The open source answer to Microsoft Teams</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com\">Nextcloud</a>.</p>\n",
    "sanitized": "When cables are cut, sanctions are put in place or privacy legislation prohibits the use of the service your entire organization depends on, what can you do?\n\n\n\nAmidst geo-political changes, organizations face dependencies on large, centralized communication platforms. A major example of this is the SaaS-only communication platform Microsoft Teams. It is the only solution on the market which deeply integrates video calls, team chat and large group call features with real-time document collaboration and file sharing, and has become critical to the functioning of many organizations. Which, in turn, has allowed Microsoft to hike prices by 20 to 40% and not face an exodus of customers – as they and their data are fully locked in.\n\n\n\nOrganisations, small and large, need a way to ensure the resiliency and digital sovereignty of their operations – an open source, privacy respecting alternative to Teams. And today, we present that solution.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nIn this short webinar, Jos walks you through how Nextcloud Talk takes on Microsoft Teams!\n\n\n\n\nWelcome to Nextcloud Talk\n\n\n\nToday, live from our Enterprise day in Paris, we launch Nextcloud Talk „Paris“. It is the only open-source solution that integrates all key features – from chats and video conferencing to webinars, complete with file sharing and office document editing – into a single platform while avoiding vendor lock-in.\n\n\n\nOur platform meets the highest standards of compliance with privacy legislations like GDPR or HIPAA and offers strict data security, ensuring full data control. Thanks to its open architecture, Talk can be seamlessly integrated into existing systems and tailored to individual needs.\n\n\n\nNextcloud Talk is designed to address three key use cases. Let’s go quickly over them!\n\n\n\n\nEfficient team chat\n\n\n\nThe integrated chat in Nextcloud Talk is designed to help teams stay connected throughout the workday. With multiple chat rooms and the ability to edit files directly within the chat, Talk streamlines hybrid team collaboration and boosts efficiency. End-to-end encryption ensures that calls remain private and secure, while integrated real-time notifications keep everyone in the loop. All data stays under your control, meeting the highest privacy and security standards.\n\n\n\nIt features deep integration with a wide variety of content. Users can add documents – and edit them right there, inline, without having to open tabs or download the file. Locations, tasks, calendars and notes can all be inserted, viewed and edited without leaving Talk.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n                    \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                            \n        \t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nVideo calls for seamless collaboration\n\n\n\nNextcloud Talk makes virtual meetings easy and accessible across devices. Whether it’s a quick check-in or a larger team meeting, our platform ensures powerful collaboration for hybrid working teams. Features like integrated whiteboards, screen sharing, and joint document editing make real-time collaboration easier than ever. Scheduling and joining calls is effortless, directly from the Nextcloud interface, integrated with the calendar app for easy scheduling of meetings.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n                    \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                            \n        \t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nInteractive webinars, education and training sessions\n\n\n\nTalk enables you to host engaging webinars – bringing audiences like teams, students, or customers together. The platform supports live streaming, Q&A sessions and screensharing and comes with moderation features. Functions like the integrated chat, animated reactions, polls and breakout rooms make the learning experience more interactive and fun. All this, and more, is available wherever you are. Not only in the browser, but also with apps on iOS and Android! When your colleague calls you while you’re out, your phone will ring and you’ll be able to share your screen to show them a quick presentation you’re working on.\n\n\n\n\t\n                    \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                                    \n                        \n                                                    \n                                            \n                            \n        \t\n\n\n\n\n\nYou can give participants a phone number to dial in to, and even pull them in by dialing out right from Talk. Need to add hundreds, even thousands of participants? Simply import a spreadsheet. After the call, you export the participant list and see who did and did not show up!\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nBreak up big groups in breakout rooms, enabling everyone to be productive in a smaller team before coming back together to the big group. In your breakout room you can do a call, chat, work on a whiteboard, share documents and more!\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nNumerous new features for better collaboration\n\n\n\nNew desktop app\n\n\n\nNo more searching through browser tabs! The new app offers desktop integration and notifications, allowing users to communicate and join calls effortlessly.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nNew AI features\n\n\n\nTired of taking notes in long meetings? Enjoy our automatically generated summaries of video meetings! Dreading those 173 unread messages in the morning? The Nextcloud Assistant summarizes them for you. Less work, less stress!\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nVisual collaboration\n\n\n\nThe interactive whiteboard enables teams to brainstorm and develop ideas in real-time – ideal for workshops and project planning.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPlan your polls\n\n\n\nYou can now save a poll as a draft, for quick publishing when the class has started. Need to use the same poll in a different class? Simply export it as a file and import it in the new room. At the end, export the poll as image or spreadsheet. Easy as pie!\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nSimplified teamwork\n\n\n\nDocuments can be collaboratively edited directly within chats or video calls. No need to switch to another window or tab! You can easily find chat messages with the search, leave and join open chat rooms or archive the ones you no longer follow, so you stay as connected as you need to be.\n\n\n\nLet colleagues know what you think with reactions to chat messages, or animated reactions during calls. And if you need to make a point, you can use bold, italics, headers and even tables in your messages.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nMindfulness features\n\n\n\n\n\n\nTo promote a healthy meeting culture, Nextcloud Talk has a series of small features that help you be mindful of yourself and others. You can send silent chat messages and even start silent calls which don’t send notifications to everyone. User status communicates to colleagues if you’re available or not – the status will automatically change when you are in a call or have an appointment in your calendar, and your time zone is visible for others.\n\n\n\nNeed to deal with something – but not right now? You can mark a chat as unread, but also set a reminder on an individual message. You’ll get a notification at the time you set! You can also send a message to a special ‘Note to self’ chat, or put notes there by hand. Keep things organized for yourself. Perhaps favorite your Note to self chat so it’s always on top with other important chats?\n\n\n\nYou can also set your work hours and enable do-not-disturb outside those hours. Calls give a warning at the 1h mark and can now automatically end after a set time. And, during calls, you can see how much each participant talked so you can make sure even the quiet team members get to have their say.\n\n\n\nHigh-security communication\n\n\n\nNextcloud Talk meets the highest security standards and can even be deployed in airgap environments, keeping all communication strictly away from the internet.\n\n\n\nDiscover more new features\nCalls:\n\n\n\n\nSummarize Call recordings automatically with AI\n\n\n\nEnforce a maximum call lenght\n\n\n\nOption to always disable devices by default\n\n\n\nOption to download a call participants list\n\n\n\nOption to blur background by default\n\n\n\n\nChat:\n\n\n\n\nSummary of chat histories when there are many unread messages\n\n\n\nOption to directly download attachments\n\n\n\nHighlight file and object shares with an icon in conversations list\n\n\n\n\nGuests:\n\n\n\n\nIdentify and recognize guests invited via mail address\n\n\n\nAllow inviting email guests when creating a conversation\n\n\n\n\nConversations:\n\n\n\n\nOption to archive conversations\n\n\n\nAutomatically lock rooms after days of inactivity\n\n\n\n\nVoice Messages:\n\n\n\n\nAuto play voice messages which are grouped together\n\n\n\n\nPolls:\n\n\n\n\nDraft, import and export polls\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nA glimpse into the future of collaboration\n\n\n\nWith Nextcloud Talk, we empower companies and public institutions to work securely and productively – regardless of their location or infrastructure. The platform is ideal for on-premises installations or hosting by local cloud providers, giving companies and organizations full control over their data.\n\n\n\nFinally, the open source community has a real answer to Microsoft Teams. \n\n\n\nLearn more at the Talk webpage, or join our upcoming webinar to find out how Talk can replace Teams for your organization!\n\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\tGet started with Nextcloud TalkLearn more about Nextcloud Talk and get started right away!\nLearn more\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\nThe post The open source answer to Microsoft Teams appeared first on Nextcloud."
