    "raw": "\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/10/MariaDB-becomes-a-sponsor-of-Nextcloud-Enterprise-Day-2024-in-Frankfurt.png\" alt=\"MariaDB becomes a sponsor of Nextcloud Enterprise Day 2024 in Frankfurt\" class=\"wp-image-264190\" srcset=\"https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/10/MariaDB-becomes-a-sponsor-of-Nextcloud-Enterprise-Day-2024-in-Frankfurt.png 1920w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/10/MariaDB-becomes-a-sponsor-of-Nextcloud-Enterprise-Day-2024-in-Frankfurt-300x169.png 300w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/10/MariaDB-becomes-a-sponsor-of-Nextcloud-Enterprise-Day-2024-in-Frankfurt-1024x576.png 1024w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/10/MariaDB-becomes-a-sponsor-of-Nextcloud-Enterprise-Day-2024-in-Frankfurt-768x432.png 768w, https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/10/MariaDB-becomes-a-sponsor-of-Nextcloud-Enterprise-Day-2024-in-Frankfurt-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:24px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p>MariaDB becomes a new sponsor of the <a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/enterprise-day/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nextcloud Enterprise Day</a> in Frankfurt on November 6.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A provider of leading open-source database solutions, MariaDB makes data easier to access and lets users focus on growing their business while being confident in their database&#8217;s resilience. A long-standing partnership between Nextcloud and MariaDB enables scalability and high availability of solutions for Nextcloud customers. We are proud to welcome MariaDB as a sponsor of the most important event for Nextcloud&#8217;s enterprise users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nextcloud Enterprise Day takes place on November 6 in Frankfurt, Germany. Register today to secure your spot!</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:24px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n<section class=\"promo-section has_custom_bg_image \" id=\"\" style=\"background-image: url(https://nextcloud.com/c/uploads/2024/08/frankfurt-sunset-skyline-1.jpg);\">\n\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Register for Nextcloud Enterprise Day today to secure your spot!</p>\n<a class=\"c-btn btn-white\" href=\"https://nextcloud.com/enterprise-day/\" target=\"_blank\">Register now</a>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:24px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About MariaDB</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>MariaDB seeks to eliminate the constraints and complexity of proprietary databases, enabling organizations to reinvest in what matters most – rapidly developing innovative, customer-facing applications. Enterprises can depend on a single complete database for all their needs, that can be deployed in minutes for transactional, analytical or hybrid use cases. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trusted by organizations such as Deutsche Bank, DBS Bank, Red Hat, ServiceNow and Samsung – MariaDB delivers customer value without the financial burden of legacy database providers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About Nextcloud Enterprise Day</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://nextcloud.com/enterprise-day/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nextcloud Enterprise Day</a> is our top event of the year for business leaders, decision-makers, and project managers to achieve their goals with Nextcloud.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>From customer presentations and success stories to networking opportunities and access to management, sales, marketing, and engineering teams, you’re bound to walk away with new information, techniques, and inspiration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The upcoming edition takes place at the spectacular Radisson Blu hotel in Frankfurt, Germany. Early Bird tickets are limited.</